1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:33,174
=Episode 20=
(Let us merge our flesh and bone.)

3
00:00:33,175 --> 00:00:35,145
(We will never to be parted again.)

4
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:49,820
(I was so foolish.)

5
00:00:50,740 --> 00:00:53,620
(I couldn't tell whether you
were human or demon.)

6
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:57,180
(Nothing can separate us now.)

7
00:00:57,540 --> 00:00:58,660
Xi.

8
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:04,340
Let us return home.

9
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:30,380
She is Xi?

10
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:39,780
Bring her back to me.

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:42,260
He is already
on the brink of exhaustion.

12
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:46,900
Today, we shall slay the god together!

13
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:01,060
Kill him!

14
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:55,100
Don't be afraid, Xi.

15
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:58,340
I'm here.

16
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,580
Do it!

17
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:17,100
Master.

18
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:26,020
- Master.
- Master.

19
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:29,739
Immortal, run!

20
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:31,020
I will cover you.

21
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,500
So it is you.

22
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:37,979
You made Zhao suffer the pain
of being devoured.

23
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:40,340
Toying with pawns

24
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:44,019
is the power of those
who wield the pieces.

25
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:45,780
What can you do to me?

26
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:49,060
What can I do to you?

27
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:58,779
Continue.

28
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:02,060
Our souls have already merged as one.

29
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:03,979
As long as the demon root
is not eradicated,

30
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:06,020
you cannot kill me.

31
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:09,020
Even if you take your own life,

32
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,899
I will follow you

33
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,780
into reincarnation.

34
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:18,179
You and I shall be together

35
00:04:18,180 --> 00:04:19,539
forever and ever.

36
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:20,900
Shut your mouth!

37
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:23,060
You shall never leave here.

38
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:26,419
Zhao almost

39
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,180
lost his life for you.

40
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:31,380
If you wish to stay longer with him,

41
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:33,500
stay away from those Flower Slaves.

42
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,500
Zhao.

43
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,657
(Lingyun Pavilion)

44
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:18,424
♪Once, the Nine Provinces shone
with brilliant lights♪

45
00:05:18,425 --> 00:05:21,949
♪For you,
I brushed the snow from your robes♪

46
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:26,832
♪I crossed mountains and seas
just to see you once♪

47
00:05:28,412 --> 00:05:31,724
♪Through countless nights
across rivers and mountains♪

48
00:05:31,725 --> 00:05:35,186
♪Yet we couldnEmperort last through the years♪

49
00:05:35,187 --> 00:05:40,070
♪This parting gathers all joy
and sorrow into silence♪

50
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:43,519
♪I too once lost myself for ages♪

51
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:47,324
♪Through love and life,
I roamed the mortal world♪

52
00:05:47,325 --> 00:05:53,359
♪Only after a fleeting century
did I learn how shallow this love was♪

53
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:56,039
♪You are the snow
that rests on timeless hills♪

54
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,161
♪You fall into my gaze♪

55
00:05:58,162 --> 00:06:00,549
♪Yet mistaken for the moon♪

56
00:06:00,550 --> 00:06:02,879
♪I break through fateEmperors cocoon♪

57
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:06,320
♪Travel a thousand miles to you♪

58
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:09,900
Your Highness.

59
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,780
The Immortal has been
unconscious for a while.

60
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,860
No one can remove the swords.

61
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,340
All the physicians in the city
are at a loss.

62
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:20,860
We can only rely on a medicinal bath
to sustain his life.

63
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:23,219
You may leave now.

64
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:23,979
But...

65
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:24,980
Leave!

66
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,620
Yes, Your Highness.

67
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:47,900
Zhao, it's me.

68
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:49,979
The swords are poisoned.

69
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:51,500
They prevent your recovery.

70
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:54,060
Be good.

71
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:56,540
Let me remove them.

72
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,420
Zhao.

73
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,900
I'm here.

74
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:56,900
I'm here.

75
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:02,060
No one will ever separate us again.

76
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:14,220
Zhao.

77
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,540
You're finally awake.

78
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:25,620
What did you just call me?

79
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,540
Zhao.

80
00:08:29,460 --> 00:08:31,500
I remember everything now.

81
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:35,300
That night...

82
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:38,180
That night must have been
despairing for you.

83
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,180
I'm sorry.

84
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,500
It's all my fault.

85
00:08:42,300 --> 00:08:43,620
I'm sorry.

86
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:46,740
It's my fault.

87
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:50,900
I couldn't tell...

88
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,180
when you have a demon heart.

89
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:59,220
Those cuts you took to save me

90
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,980
must have hurt.

91
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:05,980
It must have hurt.

92
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:09,140
It must have.

93
00:09:12,180 --> 00:09:13,260
It hurt.

94
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:17,740
It really hurt.

95
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,620
Alright.

96
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,740
I'm here.

97
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,620
I'm also here.

98
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:37,500
Come.

99
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:40,940
It's cold outside.

100
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,260
I have something for you.

101
00:09:45,687 --> 00:09:47,939
(Martial Hall)

102
00:09:47,940 --> 00:09:49,860
General, your confidential letter.

103
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:56,861
(Helian Shu colluded
with the Flower Slaves.)

104
00:09:56,862 --> 00:09:59,419
(He was stripped of his military power
and locked in the dungeon.)

105
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:01,100
(The court is becoming
more transparent.)

106
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:04,340
(I will bring Xihe
back to the palace soon.)

107
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:17,220
(Stop scratching me. It itches.)

108
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,059
Thank you, Miss Baobao,

109
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,500
for helping me find Her Highness.

110
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:25,779
Her Highness is fine now.

111
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:26,539
I will certainly

112
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:28,059
do my utmost to heal the Immortal.

113
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:30,019
I'm connected
with Master's divine power.

114
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:32,820
Now that I've transformed
into human form, he should be fine.

115
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:36,020
No need to be so formal.

116
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,980
This headband is for you.

117
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:42,620
I don't accept rewards without merit.

118
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:44,380
I...

119
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,020
I...

120
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:48,980
Do you not like it?

121
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,460
I shall take it back, then.

122
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,740
I thought you didn't want it.

123
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,160
There is no reason to give a gift
and then ask for it back.

124
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,220
Give it back to me.

125
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:43,460
Ye Zhao.

126
00:11:45,540 --> 00:11:46,820
Ye Zhao?

127
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:48,460
Why are you calling me by my full name?

128
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:51,220
The demon heart is called Hua Hui.

129
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:54,020
It contrasts greatly with your name.

130
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:55,860
Ye and Hua.
[*Leaf and flower]

131
00:11:56,660 --> 00:11:58,140
Zhao and Hui.
[*Bright and dark]

132
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,620
Zhao.

133
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:02,500
Do you have any recollection
of this name?

134
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:05,100
I have no memory before becoming a god.

135
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:08,100
Perhaps this name

136
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:11,020
is just a coincidence.

137
00:12:13,020 --> 00:12:14,500
A coincidence?

138
00:12:31,525 --> 00:12:33,234
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

139
00:12:33,235 --> 00:12:36,084
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

140
00:12:36,085 --> 00:12:38,824
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

141
00:12:38,825 --> 00:12:40,454
♪Let the long shadows♪

142
00:12:40,455 --> 00:12:46,055
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

143
00:12:46,105 --> 00:12:47,704
♪If in a dream♪

144
00:12:47,705 --> 00:12:50,464
♪I can hear your voice♪

145
00:12:50,465 --> 00:12:53,314
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

146
00:12:53,315 --> 00:12:55,914
♪Let it be us♪

147
00:12:55,915 --> 00:13:00,704
♪drawing endlessly close♪

148
00:13:00,705 --> 00:13:02,464
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

149
00:13:02,465 --> 00:13:05,115
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

150
00:13:05,335 --> 00:13:08,054
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

151
00:13:08,055 --> 00:13:09,704
♪Not even in time♪

152
00:13:09,705 --> 00:13:15,364
♪to tell you how I feel♪

153
00:13:15,365 --> 00:13:16,904
♪If the rain won't stop♪

154
00:13:16,905 --> 00:13:19,654
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

155
00:13:19,655 --> 00:13:22,624
♪Let love go on♪

156
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:25,174
♪Until forever♪

157
00:13:25,175 --> 00:13:29,814
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

158
00:13:29,815 --> 00:13:32,424
♪Until forever♪

159
00:13:32,425 --> 00:13:39,535
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
